# HMError.Code.operationTimedOut

**Case**

An error indicating the operation timed out.

## Declaration

```swift
case operationTimedOut
```

## Operation errors

- **HMError.Code.operationCancelled**: An error indicating the user canceled the operation.
- **HMError.Code.operationInProgress**: An error indicating the operation is already in progress.
